[09:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'white acrylic paint for a nice surface to print on. Since this was my first print on this machine, I needed to calibrate it, and everything looks good. So, we peeled off this paper from the large flatbed, and then applied this grippy top layer that helps keep your'

[09:50] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'objects in place. Then I put my canvas onto the flatbed, and we\'re ready to print. In the software, I took a snapshot of my object, and the printer started automatically measuring the canvas. Then I brought in this painting I did and used the built-in tools to get'

[10:03] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'it into the correct position. I wanted to do this one as a raised print using Uvi make E1\'s raised printing algorithm to analyze my art and find out which area should pop out more than others. I hit print in the software, then the'

[10:16] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'printer did its thing for a second, and then I hit this big, satisfying start button. Then away the printer went, and I walked off to start on my handsaw. &gt;&gt; Can\'t wait to give the boys a brand new bowl.'

